==Demographics==
<!-- As of the [[census]] of 2000, there were 97 people, 37 households, and 27 families residing in the CDP. The population density was {{convert|121.0|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. There were 43 housing units at an average density of {{convert|53.6|/sqmi|/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of the CDP was 86.60% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]], 1.03% [[Pacific Islander (U.S. Census)|Pacific Islander]], 10.31% from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 2.06% from two or more races. [[Hispanic (U.S. Census)|Hispanic]] or [[Latino (U.S. Census)|Latino]] of any race were 11.34% of the population.

